  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe and the United States of America (USA). The aim of the
      trial is to assess clinical efficacy and safety of NNC0114-0006 in subjects with active
      Crohn's disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
